OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGovernment to shorten HGV  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdriver testing process     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government is expected to announce 
OL,6, a shake-up of the HGV driver testing   
OL,7, process as soon as Thursday.           
OL,9,FIt wants fast track drivers into the   
OL,10,Fhaulage industry amid chronic shortages
OL,11,Fwhich have caused supply problems.     
OL,13,FThe BBC understands that during        
OL,14,Fmeetings between government officials, 
OL,15,Fhauliers and suppliers, the "penny     
OL,16,Ffinally dropped" that the driver       
OL,17,Fshortage was getting worse not better. 
OL,19,FThe government said meetings with      
OL,20,Faffected groups were ongoing.          
